(5, 5, 1, 'Is it Good t Have less friends?', NULL, 'It is actually better to have less number of friends that way you can remember about their family members and their frnds circle without facing any difficulty.', '<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Actually it\'s better to have less friends. Make small number of friends but make good ones. The one ready to turn everything for you. Actually the people who you think have a lot of friends ,usually have same number of less friends like you, but they hang around with many people and are good pretenders. In a friend circle of 10-12 people, they can rely upon only a few.</span><br style=\"color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Also when you have a lot of friends you can\'t meet their expectations sometime. (Happens with me)</span><br style=\"color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">That doesn\'t mean that you decide to be a loner, but do try to make small but long term friends.</span></p>', 'posts/December2019/vYv0F13e81Tv3ZktZwow.jpg', 'is-it-good-t-have-less-friends', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED', 1, '2019-11-07 06:38:32', '2019-12-10 17:33:37', 19),
(6, 1, 3, 'How does it feel to have no friends as an adult and no social life?', NULL, 'Just like people avoid a financially bankrupt person who has nothing to give to others and who can only suck other people’s wealth, people also avoid emotionally bankrupt people who have nothing to offer and everything to demand.', '<p class=\"ui_qtext_para u-ltr u-text-align--start\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; direction: ltr !important;\">Let me explain it now.</p>\r\n<p class=\"ui_qtext_para u-ltr u-text-align--start\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; direction: ltr !important;\">Suppose you belong to a rich family and you got 1,000,000 inheritance in your bank account.</p>\r\n<p class=\"ui_qtext_para u-ltr u-text-align--start\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; direction: ltr !important;\">You are so happy to have such a fat bank balance that you decide to enjoy your life by splurging all the inheritance.</p>\r\n<p class=\"ui_qtext_para u-ltr u-text-align--start\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; direction: ltr !important;\">Instead of investing this money in a productive way, or working regularly to earn income of your own, you exhausted all the inheritance and lived life king size unmindful of the future.</p>\r\n<p class=\"ui_qtext_para u-ltr u-text-align--start\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; direction: ltr !important;\">Very soon, you are going to become&nbsp;<strong>financially bankrupt</strong>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"ui_qtext_para u-ltr u-text-align--start\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; direction: ltr !important;\">In the same way, when you exhaust all your emotional inheritance and fail to earn emotional merit of your own, you become emotionally bankrupt. Thereafter,</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 2em 1em 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px 0px 0.7em; position: relative;\">You would have no friend.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px 0px 0.7em; position: relative;\">You would have no social life.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px 0px 0.7em; position: relative;\">No one would take you out.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">No one would offer you tea, coffee etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"ui_qtext_para u-ltr u-text-align--start\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; direction: ltr !important;\"><strong>Just like people avoid a financially bankrupt person who has nothing to give to others and who can only suck other people&rsquo;s wealth, people also avoid emotionally bankrupt people who have nothing to offer and everything to demand</strong>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"ui_qtext_para u-ltr u-text-align--start\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; direction: ltr !important;\">Don&rsquo;t take relationships for granted.</p>\r\n<p class=\"ui_qtext_para u-ltr u-text-align--start\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; direction: ltr !important;\">You need to regularly water every relationship to keep it alive and bear fruits to fulfill your emotional needs.</p>\r\n<p class=\"ui_qtext_para u-ltr u-text-align--start\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; direction: ltr !important;\">It is never too late to build new relationships.</p>\r\n<p class=\"ui_qtext_para u-ltr u-text-align--start\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; direction: ltr !important;\">Start caring for other people now and they shall care you back.</p>\r\n<p class=\"ui_qtext_para u-ltr u-text-align--start\" style=\"padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; direction: ltr !important; margin: 0px 0px 0px !important 0px;\">You would soon build strong and lasting relationships in the world to live a happy life.</p>', 'posts/December2019/ctdV1AWnrEIsJ6o7GmPi.jpg', 'how-does-it-feel-to-have-no-friends-as-an-adult-and-no-social-life', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED', 1, '2019-11-07 06:40:21', '2019-12-10 17:38:32', 48),
(7, 1, 1, 'Fact Check: This is not Bruce Lee playing ping-pong with Nunchaku', NULL, 'Many people on social media are astounded and amused by a video clip where a martial artist is expertly playing ping-pong with a Nunchaku -- a traditional martial art weapon rather than a paddle. The clip has been posted and shared by many on Facebook claiming that this is the rare clip of martial arts star Bruce Lee playing ping-pong with Nunchaku in 1970.', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; padding: 17px 0px 0px; font-size: 17px; line-height: 29px; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-height: 800px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; color: #000000; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif;\"><strong>Many</strong> people on social media are astounded and amused by a video clip where a martial artist is expertly playing ping-pong with a Nunchaku -- a traditional martial art weapon rather than a paddle.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 17px; line-height: 29px; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-height: 800px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; color: #000000; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif;\">The black and white clip has been posted and shared by many on Facebook claiming that this is the rare clip of martial arts star Bruce Lee playing ping-pong with Nunchaku in 1970.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.8rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 17px; line-height: 29px; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-height: 800px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; color: #000000; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif;\">Users like Sumita Chakraborty posted this clip recently on Facebook, saying, \"A priceless clip of 1970 of Bruce Lee playing Table Tennis with his Nan-chak !! His focus on speed, reflexes and accuracy was absolutely incredible\"</p>', 'posts/December2019/9m4dlKqW6SWtQXN7m344.jpg', 'fact-check-this-is-not-bruce-lee-playing-ping-pong-with-nunchaku', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2019-11-08 02:35:15', '2019-12-10 17:34:19', 4),
(8, 1, 1, 'Misleading comparison between Statue of Unity and Taj Mahal goes viral', NULL, 'The Statue of Unity, dedicated to Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel, was inaugurated by Prime Minister Narendra Modi in Gujarat last year. At 182 metres, it is the world’s tallest statue. However, there has been criticism from various quarters over the amount of money spent to build the monument.', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #000000; font-family: OpenSans-Regular; font-size: 17px;\"><strong>The</strong> Statue of Unity, dedicated to Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel, was inaugurated by Prime Minister Narendra Modi in Gujarat last year. At 182 metres, it is the world&rsquo;s tallest statue. However, there has been criticism from various quarters over the amount of money spent to build the monument.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #000000; font-family: OpenSans-Regular; font-size: 17px;\">As the Statue of Unity completed a year of the inauguration on October 31, social media is filled with posts as to how it has turned into a bigger tourist attraction than the Taj Mahal and earned thrice the revenue than the Monument of Love&rsquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #000000; font-family: OpenSans-Regular; font-size: 17px;\">Facebook page Global Hindus&rsquo; stated some figures to claim that the Statue of Unity attracted more tourists and earned thrice the Taj Mahal&rsquo;s average annual turnover in 2019. India Today Anti Fake News War Room (AFWA) has found the claim to be misleading.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #000000; font-family: OpenSans-Regular; font-size: 17px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Taj Mahal stats</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #000000; font-family: OpenSans-Regular; font-size: 17px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #000000; font-family: OpenSans-Regular; font-size: 17px;\">Facebook page Global Hindus&rsquo;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</strong>has claimed that the Statue of Unity attracted 26 lakh tourists and earned Rs 71.6 crore in 2019. It went on to say that in the last three years, the Taj Mahal&rsquo;s average annual visitor was 7.50 lakh and the average annual turnover was Rs 22.3 crore. The archived version of the post can be seen&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: #026bc5; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\" href=\"http://archive.is/7vljb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #000000; font-family: OpenSans-Regular; font-size: 17px;\">We found a&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: #026bc5; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\" href=\"http://164.100.24.220/loksabhaquestions/annex/171/AU2474.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">document</a>&nbsp;</strong>of the ministry of culture where all details related to Taj Mahal and other monuments in India can be found. It is basically an answer given in the Lok Sabha on July 8, 2019.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #000000; font-family: OpenSans-Regular; font-size: 17px;\">According to the ministry data, in 2018-19, Taj Mahal attracted more than 68 lakh visitors and earned more than Rs 77 crore in entry fees.</p>', 'posts/December2019/4gfuAzHt73p1pLHuJe7P.jpg', 'misleading-comparison-between-statue-of-unity-and-taj-mahal-goes-viral', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2019-11-08 02:40:19', '2019-12-10 17:07:07', 12),
(9, 1, 1, 'Governor, Police, Media Reports Belie Amit Shah’s ‘Not A Single Bullet Or Tear Gas’ Claim', NULL, 'Govt authorities admit pellet injuries\r\n\r\nThe governor of Jammu and Kashmir, Satya Pal Malik, “admitted use of pellet guns by security personnel during protests in the Kashmir Valley”, further adding that “forces took utmost precaution to prevent injuries”, as per a report by the news agency PTI published by various newspapers including the Business Standard on August 28, 2019.\r\n\r\n“It\'s our achievement that there has been no civilian casualties so far. There were allegations that we are concealing the number of deaths but on the contrary we are sharing information even on pellet injuries. Barring one case, all pellet injuries were below the waist, only one person was hit in the neck, he is also fine and out of danger now,” The Hindu quoted the J&K governor in this August 28, 2019, report.\r\n\r\nThe Jammu and Kashmir Police are also on record stating that people were treated for pellet injuries. “There have been a few pellet injuries, they were treated,” Munir Ahmed Khan, additional director-general of police (ADGP), law and order, Kashmir, said, ANI reported on August 14, 2019.', '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Mumbai</span>: Not a single bullet or tear gas has been fired in Kashmir, not a single person has died, since the abrogation of Article 370 on August 5, 2019, home minister Amit Shah&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://twitter.com/ANI/status/1168258481750568960\">claimed</a>&nbsp;on September 1, 2019. However, this claim is belied by statements by the Jammu &amp; Kashmir (J&amp;K) Governor and the state police, as well as journalists&rsquo; accounts from Srinagar, including this&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.boomlive.in/i-spent-nine-days-in-kashmir-fact-checking-the-governments-claims-of-normalcy/\">report</a>&nbsp;in fact-checking website&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">BOOM.</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">Here&rsquo;s a fact-check of the home minister&rsquo;s claim from various sources:</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Claim</span>: &ldquo;Since the abrogation of Article 370, not a single bullet or tear gas has been fired in Kashmir, not a single person has died,&rdquo; Amit Shah, home minister of India,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://twitter.com/BJP4India/status/1168176396411162625\">said</a>&nbsp;during a rally in Maharashtra&rsquo;s Solapur on September 1, 2019.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Fact:</span>&nbsp;False. Government authorities--governor of J&amp;K and the police--have admitted the use of pellet guns and injuries, media reports (<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/36-suffered-pellet-injuries-since-august-5-official/article29280622.ece\">here</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://twitter.com/ANI/status/1161515103524667392\">here</a>) said.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Media report firing of tear gas and pellet shots</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">At least 152 people suffered injuries from tear gas and pellets fired by the security forces in Kashmir,&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Reuters</em>&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://in.reuters.com/article/india-kashmir-injuries/key-hospitals-in-kashmir-treat-more-than-150-tear-gas-pellet-injuries-idINKCN1VD0F3\">reported</a>&nbsp;on August 23, 2019, citing data from the Sher-i-Kashmir Institute of Medical Sciences and Shri Maharaja Hari Singh Hospital between August 5 and 21, 2019.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">The report said there had been protests including stone-pelting by locals, especially youths, after gatherings such as for Friday prayers, and that the security forces had fired in retaliation.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Indian police used tear gas and pellets to fight back at least 10,000 people protesting Delhi&rsquo;s withdrawal of special rights for Muslim-majority Jammu and Kashmir state in its main city of Srinagar on Friday, a police official and two witnesses said,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Reuters</em>&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://in.reuters.com/article/india-kashmir-370/thousands-protest-in-kashmir-over-new-status-despite-clampdown-idINKCN1UZ0OO\">reported</a>&nbsp;earlier on August 9, 2019.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">Around 280 law and order incidents had taken place across 10 districts in the Kashmir valley,&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The Indian Express</em>&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/india/jammu-and-kashmir-law-and-order-incidents-srinagar-tops-the-list-jk-police-report-5952774/\">reported</a>&nbsp;on August 31, 2019, citing an internal report of J&amp;K Police.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">At least 80 people have sustained pellet injuries in these incidents, the report said, adding that Srinagar had reported more than 160 law-and-order incidents between August 5 and 27, followed by 22 incidents in Pulwama and 18 in Baramulla.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">On August 9, 2019, there were large protests in Soura, about 11 km north of Lal Chowk in Srinagar, the international media reported. The BBC released a&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/av/49306816/article-370-tear-gas-at-kashmir-rally-india-denies-happened\">video</a>&nbsp;purportedly showing protestors trying to escape from security forces&rsquo; retaliatory fire.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">A report from the ground</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;There have been incidents of protests every Friday in Soura since the abrogation of Article 370,&rdquo; Nivedita Niranjankumar, deputy editor-south with&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">BOOM</em>, who visited Srinagar from August 14-22, 2019, told&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">FactChecker.in</span>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;I saw forces firing tear gas in downtown area after residents pelted stones at the forces in the afternoon of August 17,&rdquo; Niranjankumar&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.boomlive.in/i-spent-nine-days-in-kashmir-fact-checking-the-governments-claims-of-normalcy/\">wrote</a>&nbsp;in&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">BOOM</em>&nbsp;on August 25, 2019. &ldquo;In most areas, stones are met with pellets and tear gas and lockdowns met with slogans.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;While I was covering the situation on the ground with a fellow journalist, there was an incident where tear gas was fired during the protest, due to which I had a burning sensation in my eyes from the smoke it released, because of which we had to quickly move away from that area,&rdquo; Niranjankumar told&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">FactChecker.in</span>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">Niranjankumar said she had also spoken to a 17-year-old in Srinagar, who had sustained pellet injuries during the August 9, 2019, protests in Soura. &ldquo;The pellets entered my thigh and some went through to the other thigh. The doctors have said they cannot remove many of the pellets but it is to be seen how my body functions after this,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">BOOM</em>&nbsp;had&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.boomlive.in/i-spent-nine-days-in-kashmir-fact-checking-the-governments-claims-of-normalcy/\">quoted</a>&nbsp;the person as saying.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">On August 20, 2019, the BBC released another&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/av/world-asia-49408355/kashmir-unrest-they-shot-me-and-i-fell-to-the-ground\">video</a>, of persons allegedly injured in retaliatory action by the security forces. \"I am injured right now but once I recover I will join the protests again,\" one of them said.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Death reports contested</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">Asrar Khan, a 16-year old youth who was allegedly injured by pellets and tear gas shells on August 6, 2019, outside his home in Srinagar, died on September 3, 2019, Al Jazeera&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2019/09/kashmiri-teenager-dies-pellet-tear-gas-shell-wounds-hospital-190904181621345.html\">reported</a>&nbsp;on September 5, 2019. Earlier, on August 9, 2019,&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Al Jazeera</em>&nbsp;had&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2019/08/kashmiris-fighting-lives-pellet-gun-attacks-190808105704499.html\">reported</a>&nbsp;about Asrar&rsquo;s injury and his treatment at a hospital.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">The security forces have contested this report. &ldquo;The credibility of Al Jazeera is zero,&rdquo; said ADGP Munir Khan, replying to a reporter&rsquo;s question on&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Al Jazeera&rsquo;s</em>&nbsp;report at a joint briefing of the Indian Army and J&amp;K Police on September 4, 2019. &ldquo;The channel has been reporting wrong things right from day one. The channel has been trying to instigate violence in Kashmir right from day one. So we don\'t believe the channel. We have our local channels why don\'t they report like him [the&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Al Jazeera</em>&nbsp;reporter],&rdquo; Khan said.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;We categorically reject [Munir Khan&rsquo;s] allegations and stand by the quality and accuracy of our journalism,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Al Jazeera</em>&nbsp;said in a&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://network.aljazeera.net/pressroom/al-jazeera-rejects-accusations-munir-khan-additional-director-general-police-law-and-order\">statement</a>&nbsp;on September 5, 2019.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">In an another incident, 17-year-old Osaib Altaf from Srinagar&rsquo;s Palpora was&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.huffingtonpost.in/entry/kashmir-first-civilian-casualty-after-article-370-revoked_in_5d4ab624e4b0066eb70aaca3\">reported</a>&nbsp;to have drowned in a river while trying to escape the Central Reserve Police Force (CRPF) on August 5, 2019, in&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The Huffington Post</em>&nbsp;on August 7, 2019. The report called him &ldquo;Kashmir&rsquo;s first casualty&rdquo; after the abrogation of Article 370. Altaf was among some boys playing near a playground &ldquo;when they were chased&rdquo; away by the CRPF, the report said.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img title=\"booking\" src=\"http://laravel.test/storage/posts/November2019/Boom.jpg\" alt=\"new\" />\r\n<figcaption>Caption</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;The Union Home Ministry refused to comment or clarify on the incident,&rdquo; the&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Hindustan Times</em>&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: #4092c3; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/16-year-old-drowns-in-jhelum-after-alleged-chase-by-crpf-personnel/story-9oUP4D6bVvBOpdx2QMOzyK.html\">reported</a>&nbsp;on August 8, 2019. &ldquo;Policemen drawn from several paramilitary forces are deployed. The CRPF is not responsible for any such incident, a senior CRPF official said.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #555555; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>', 'posts/December2019/3co77D5zT099P2CAkJj2.jpg', 'governor-police-media-reports-belie-amit-shah-s-not-a-single-bullet-or-tear-gas-claim', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2019-11-08 02:46:04', '2019-12-10 15:01:55', 19);
