(25, 1, 8, 'Several artists from the Middle East couldn’t attend their own MoMA PS1 show due to the travel ban and other diplomatic issues.', NULL, '“Theater of Operations” to protest Museum of Modern Art board trustee Larry Fink’s investments in private prison companies, according to a Hyperallergic report. Collins is a England-born and Berlin-based artist, so he was not subject to the travel ban.', '<div class=\"NewsSections__NewsSectionContainer-sk8dx2-0 lfBUcC\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: \'Adobe Garamond W08\', adobe-garamond-pro, AGaramondPro-Regular, \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 17px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 660px; color: #000000;\">\r\n<div class=\"article__text-section StyledText-sc-1ysl1h-0 iMEKdP\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; width: 660px;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: black; cursor: pointer; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.3); text-decoration-line: none; background-image: linear-gradient(transparent 0px, #333333 1px, transparent 0px); background-size: 1.25px 4px; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-position: center bottom;\" href=\"https://www.artsy.net/moma-ps1\">MoMA PS1</a>&rsquo;s newest show, &ldquo;Theater of Operations: The Gulf Wars, 1991&ndash;2011,&rdquo; explores the legacy of U.S. interventions in the Middle East and features work by dozens of artists from the region. But several of the artists in the exhibition were unable to attend its opening last weekend due to U.S. President Donald Trump&rsquo;s travel ban.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1em 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">According to&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: black; cursor: pointer; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.3); text-decoration-line: none; background-image: linear-gradient(transparent 0px, #333333 1px, transparent 0px); background-size: 1.25px 4px; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-position: center bottom;\" href=\"https://news.artnet.com/art-world/middle-eastern-visa-denied-1697532\">artnet News</a></em>, at least four artists who tried to get travel visas were denied due to the travel ban or other diplomatic issues. And other artists didn&rsquo;t even try to get visas, knowing that they would not be allowed entry. One artist was questioned when they arrived to the United States, but was still able to come to the opening. Among the artists who were unable to make the opening were the Iraqi artists Ali Eyal and&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: black; cursor: pointer; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.3); text-decoration-line: none; background-image: linear-gradient(transparent 0px, #333333 1px, transparent 0px); background-size: 1.25px 4px; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-position: center bottom;\" href=\"https://www.artsy.net/artist/afifa-aleiby\">Afifa Aleiby</a>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1em 0px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Ruba Katrib, one of the show&rsquo;s curators, told&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">artnet News</em>:</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"NewsSections__NewsSectionContainer-sk8dx2-0 lfBUcC\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: \'Adobe Garamond W08\', adobe-garamond-pro, AGaramondPro-Regular, \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 17px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 660px; color: #000000;\">\r\n<div class=\"article__text-section StyledText-sc-1ysl1h-0 iMEKdP\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; width: 660px;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n<blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: auto; padding: 10px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: Unica77LLWebMedium, Arial, serif; font-size: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1.5em; word-break: break-word; max-width: 560px;\">More would have wanted to come, but knew there was no way. Artwork is able to travel more easily in some cases than the artists themselves.</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"NewsSections__NewsSectionContainer-sk8dx2-0 lfBUcC\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: \'Adobe Garamond W08\', adobe-garamond-pro, AGaramondPro-Regular, \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 17px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 660px; color: #000000;\">\r\n<div class=\"article__text-section StyledText-sc-1ysl1h-0 iMEKdP\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; width: 660px;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">The travel ban has been in place since December 2017, and was instituted by a presidential order, though the U.S. Supreme Court affirmed it in a 5&ndash;4 decision. The ban indefinitely suspends immigrant and non-immigrant visa applications from Libya, Iran, Somalia, Syria, Yemen, North Korea, and Venezuela.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1em 0px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">In addition to the artists based in Iraq and its diasporas, &ldquo;Theater of Operations&rdquo; includes Western artists responding to the conflicts. One such artist,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: black; cursor: pointer; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.3); text-decoration-line: none; background-image: linear-gradient(transparent 0px, #333333 1px, transparent 0px); background-size: 1.25px 4px; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-position: center bottom;\" href=\"https://www.artsy.net/artist/phil-collins\">Phil Collins</a>, withdrew his video work&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">baghdad screentests</em>&nbsp;(2002) from &ldquo;Theater of Operations&rdquo; to protest&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: black; cursor: pointer; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.3); text-decoration-line: none; background-image: linear-gradient(transparent 0px, #333333 1px, transparent 0px); background-size: 1.25px 4px; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-position: center bottom;\" href=\"https://www.artsy.net/museum-of-modern-art\">Museum of Modern Art</a>&nbsp;board trustee Larry Fink&rsquo;s investments in private prison companies, according to a&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: black; cursor: pointer; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.3); text-decoration-line: none; background-image: linear-gradient(transparent 0px, #333333 1px, transparent 0px); background-size: 1.25px 4px; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-position: center bottom;\" href=\"https://hyperallergic.com/525594/phil-collins-moma-ps1/\">Hyperallergic</a></em>&nbsp;report. Collins is a England-born and Berlin-based artist, so he was not subject to the travel ban.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'posts/December2019/YLORJneN2ARwJJOrXOTp.jpg', 'several-artists-from-the-middle-east-couldn-t-attend-their-own-moma-ps1-show-due-to-the-travel-ban-and-other-diplomatic-issues', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2019-11-08 03:30:40', '2019-12-03 11:52:07', NULL),
(26, 1, 3, '“Theater of Operations” to protest Museum of Modern Art board trustee Larry Fink’s investments in private prison companies, according to a Hyperallergic report. Collins is a England-born and Berlin-based artist, so he was not subject to the travel ban.', NULL, '“I think he understands what it feels like to be left out so he wants to include everybody and just to tell everybody he loves them,” Kerry told BBC.', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Since 21-year-old David Bloch is mostly nonverbal, he doesn&rsquo;t often say things to his parents&mdash;and since the autistic young man also has a rare immunodeficiency disorder, he rarely spends much time outdoors.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">This means that David doesn&rsquo;t really have any friends in his hometown of Neptune Beach, Florida. He has been homeschooled his entire life, and he hasn&rsquo;t spent much time around other people his own age.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">But after he recently asked his mother a question for the first time in his life, he has made thousands of friends all over the world.</p>\r\n<div class=\"td-a-rec td-a-rec-id-content_inlineleft  td_uid_33_5dc522e3e34cb_rand td_block_template_1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; float: left; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">\r\n<div class=\"desktop-left\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; float: left; margin: 2px 20px 10px 2px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">David and his mother Kerry were watching television together earlier this week when he asked her a simple, but heart-wrenching question: &ldquo;Would someone like me?&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">&ldquo;I was flabbergasted,&rdquo; she&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #4db2ec; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-50310275\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">told BBC</a>. &ldquo;That&rsquo;s the first question he has ever said to me. I left the room because I had to cry. I didn&rsquo;t want David to think I was upset.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Upon regaining her composure, Kerry told her son that there were &ldquo;thousands of people&rdquo; out there who would like him. She was so moved by the conversation, she later made a Twitter post about the incident and shared it with her few hundred social media followers&mdash;and she was stunned by the response.</p>\r\n<div class=\"SandboxRoot env-bp-350\" style=\"max-height: 10000px; direction: ltr; background: 0px 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; font-family: Helvetica, Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', Calibri, sans-serif; color: #1c2022; white-space: initial; position: relative;\" data-twitter-event-id=\"0\">\r\n<div id=\"twitter-widget-0\" class=\"EmbeddedTweet EmbeddedTweet--cta js-clickToOpenTarget\" lang=\"en\" style=\"overflow: 