(28, 1, 11, 'Nurse Adopted Man With Autism After Knowing Him Just 2 Days So He Could Receive a Heart Transplant', NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">This compassionate nurse is responsible for saving the life of a 27-year-old man with autism after she volunteered to become his legal guardian just two days after meeting him.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Lori Wood, who is an ICU nurse at Piedmont Newnan Hospital in Georgia, first met Jonathan Pinkard after she was assigned to his care back in December 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Pinkard was in desperate need of a heart transplant&mdash;but since his grandmother passed away several years earlier and his mother was in rehab, he was ineligible for the transplant list.</p>\r\n<div class=\"td-a-rec td-a-rec-id-content_inlineleft  td_uid_33_5dc503cdc75db_rand td_block_template_1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; float: left; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">\r\n<div class=\"desktop-left\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; float: left; margin: 2px 20px 10px 2px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">This is because&mdash;with thousands of people waiting on transplant lists every year&mdash;doctors require organ recipients to have stable support systems so that patients are guaranteed to have someone to take care of them after an operation.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">LOOK</span>:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #4db2ec; text-decoration-line: none;\" title=\"When Pup&rsquo;s Death Left Man Heartbroken, He Healed By Adopting 8 Senior Dogs That No One Wanted\" href=\"https://www.goodnewsnetwork.org/man-healed-from-pups-death-by-adopting-8-senior-dogs/\" rel=\"bookmark\">When Pup&rsquo;s Death Left Man Heartbroken, He Healed By Adopting 8 Senior Dogs That No One Wanted</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">So for four months, Pinkard was in and out of the hospital without hope of receiving a heart. Not only that, he was often discharged to a men&rsquo;s shelter because he had nowhere else to go.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Thankfully, his luck changed after he met Wood.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Pinkard and Wood quickly bonded over their love of football and&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Family Feud&mdash;</em>and as the 57-year-old nurse became more and more familiar with her patient&rsquo;s circumstances, she knew she had to help him.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">MORE</span>:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #4db2ec; text-decoration-line: none;\" title=\"Policeman Moved by Plea for Parenthood Adopts Baby of Drug-Addicted Homeless Woman\" href=\"https://www.goodnewsnetwork.org/policeman-adopts-baby-of-drug-addicted-homeless-woman/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Policeman Moved by Plea for Parenthood Adopts Baby of Drug-Addicted Homeless Woman</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Two days after meeting Pinkard, Wood offered to adopt him and become his legal guardian so he could be placed on the transplant list. Needless to say, he accepted.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Pinkard underwent a successful heart transplant back in August. Wood&mdash;who Pinkard affectionately calls &ldquo;mama&rdquo;&mdash;has been monitoring the young man&rsquo;s various medications and caring for him after his operation. She has even been teaching him different life skills so he might one day live more independently.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">When Piedmont Healthcare asked Wood about her decision to adopt Pinkard, she simply said: &ldquo;When you&rsquo;re a nurse and you&rsquo;re wanting to fix and help people, that can be very frustrating. At some point, God places people in situations in your life, and you have the choice to do something about it. And I guess &hellip; for this situation there was no choice. It really wasn&rsquo;t anything I struggled about. He had to come home with me.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">If you want to help finance Pinkard&rsquo;s medical expenses and hospital transportation, you can donate to his&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #4db2ec; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/yqzt4-3000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">GoFundMe campaign</a>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">(<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">WATCH</span>&nbsp;the inspiring hospital video below)</p>\r\n<p><iframe style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; overflow: hidden;\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPiedmontHealthcare%2Fvideos%2F979757202367945%2F&amp;show_text=0&amp;width=560\" width=\"560\" height=\"316\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">Be Sure And Share This Sweet Story With Your Friends On Social Media&hellip;</span></p>', 'posts/December2019/PvWKTiMRhyzUgt2ny8Rh.jpg', 'nurse-adopted-man-with-autism-after-knowing-him-just-2-days-so-he-could-receive-a-heart-transplant', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2019-11-08 03:36:42', '2019-12-10 15:04:25', 18),
(29, 1, 11, 'After 4 Years of Sending Messages to Her Late Father’s Phone Number, She Suddenly Gets a Reassuring Text Back', NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">It&rsquo;s been four years since Chastity Patterson lost her beloved father figure&mdash;and just as she was finally preparing to let go of her grief, she got an astonishing text message out of the blue&hellip;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Jason Lignon passed away in 2015, and though he wasn&rsquo;t her &lsquo;biological&rsquo; dad, he had never missed a school dance or sporting event, and became a role model for her&mdash;and her friends&mdash;doling out love and advice.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">&ldquo;Blood could not make him any closer,&rdquo;&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #4db2ec; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chastity.patterson/posts/10211935324258797\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">writes</a>&nbsp;Patterson. &ldquo;I&rsquo;ve cried with him, told him everything, and even became very independent because he took the time to love me and show me what happiness looks like.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<div class=\"td-a-rec td-a-rec-id-content_inlineleft  td_uid_33_5dc503411bf82_rand td_block_template_1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; float: left; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">\r\n<div class=\"desktop-left\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; float: left; margin: 2px 20px 10px 2px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Through four years of college, the 23-year-old has been texting Jason&rsquo;s old phone number every day, sending him messages about her life, telling him about her challenges and troubles.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Finally the day came in October when she felt ready to let go. On eve of the fourth anniversary of his death, she texted him one last time recapping everything he&rsquo;d missed&mdash;how she overcame cancer and graduated college.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">After summing up her feelings, Patterson finally concluded her text by saying that she would always love and miss him&mdash;so imagine her surprise when she suddenly got a text message back.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">It said: &ldquo;Hi sweetheart, I am not your father, but I have been getting all your messages for the past 4 years. I look forward to your morning messages and nightly updates.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">&ldquo;My name is Brad and I lost my daughter in a car wreck August 2014 and your messages have kept me alive. When you text me, I know it&rsquo;s a message from God.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">MORE</span>:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #4db2ec; text-decoration-line: none;\" title=\"Anonymous Postal Worker Sent Girl a Sweet Package After She Addressed a Letter to &lsquo;God&rsquo; About Her Dog in Heaven\" href=\"https://www.goodnewsnetwork.org/girl-surprised-with-package-from-god-after-writing-letter-about-dog-in-heaven/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Anonymous Postal Worker Sent Girl a Sweet Package After She Addressed a Letter to &lsquo;God&rsquo; About Her Dog in Heaven</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">&ldquo;I&rsquo;m sorry you lost someone so close to you, but I have listened to you over the years and I have watched you grow&mdash;and go through more than anyone,&rdquo; it continued. &ldquo;I have wanted to text you back for years, but I didn&rsquo;t want to break your heart.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">&ldquo;You are an extraordinary woman and I wish my daughter would have become the woman you are.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">&ldquo;I&rsquo;m sorry you have to go through this but if it makes it any better, I am very proud of you!&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p><iframe style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; overflow: hidden;\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchastity.patterson%2Fposts%2F10211925503173276&amp;width=500\" width=\"500\" height=\"688\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Needless to say, Chastity was in awe of the response&mdash;and shared the messages&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #4db2ec; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chastity.patterson/posts/10211935324258797\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">on Facebook</a>&nbsp;hoping that other grieving people might find peace from the serendipitous message reassuring her that everything was going to be alright.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">&ldquo;Today was my sign that everything is okay and I can let him rest!&rdquo; she exclaimed.</p>', 'posts/December2019/sKRNvxtKyLa1dqkj9vEW.jpg', 'after-4-years-of-sending-messages-to-her-late-father-s-phone-number-she-suddenly-gets-a-reassuring-text-back', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2019-11-08 03:38:13', '2019-12-10 14:58:59', 4),
(30, 1, 11, 'Dozens of Volunteers Answer the World’s Most Forlorn Love Letters Addressed to Shakespeare’s Juliet By McKinley Corbley -Nov 3, 2019', NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Dozens of volunteers have been offering romantic advice to the world&rsquo;s most lovelorn souls&mdash;and they&rsquo;ve been doing it all on behalf of William Shakespeare&rsquo;s most iconic heroine.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #4db2ec; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"http://www.julietclub.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The Juliet Club</em></a>&nbsp;is a nonprofit organization that responds to letters that have been sent to Juliet Capulet, the tragic figure in Shakespeare&rsquo;s&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Romeo and Juliet</em>&nbsp;which takes place in Verona, Italy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Addressed simply to &ldquo;Juliet, Verona&rdquo; thousands of letters arrive from all over the world from people lamenting their various romantic woes and heartache&mdash;and the Juliet Club volunteers have always done their best to offer up some valuable advice in return.</p>\r\n<div class=\"td-a-rec td-a-rec-id-content_inlineleft  td_uid_33_5dc5229d94f1d_rand td_block_template_1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; float: left; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">\r\n<div class=\"desktop-left\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; float: left; margin: 2px 20px 10px 2px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">RELATED</span>:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #4db2ec; text-decoration-line: none;\" title=\"Divorce Lawyer Shares What He&rsquo;s Learned From Failed Marriages &ndash;and Why He Still Believes It&rsquo;s a Good Idea\" href=\"https://www.goodnewsnetwork.org/divorce-lawyer-shares-what-hes-learned-from-failed-marriages-and-why-he-still-believes-its-a-good-idea/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Divorce Lawyer Shares What He&rsquo;s Learned From Failed Marriages &ndash;and Why He Still Believes It&rsquo;s a Good Idea</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">41-year-old Martin Hopley&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #4db2ec; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-49904433\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">told BBC</a>&nbsp;that he has now been a Juliet Club volunteer for several years, motivated to continue after receiving a response to one of his own replies based on his experience with a particularly devastating breakup.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">Hopley says that he often takes several days to respond to some of the letters because he wants to send them the most thoughtful answers possible.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">The club hosts a multitude of writers who have had a variety of unique relationship experiences so they can respond to every different form of inquiry.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">LOOK</span>:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #4db2ec; text-decoration-line: none;\" title=\"Bride and Groom Betrothed to History After She Wore a Wedding Dress Made From the Parachute That Saved Him\" href=\"https://www.goodnewsnetwork.org/wedding-dress-made-from-parachute-that-saved-groom/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Bride and Groom Betrothed to History After She Wore a Wedding Dress Made From the Parachute That Saved Him</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">&ldquo;From the woman who&rsquo;s fallen in love with a close friend, to the man whose wife has passed away, to the boy who&rsquo;s coming to terms with his sexuality, to the girl who doesn&rsquo;t believe she&rsquo;s beautiful enough to find love&hellip; Juliet has probably heard every possible scenario you can think of,&rdquo; Hopley&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #4db2ec; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-49904433\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">told BBC</a>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">&ldquo;When people write to Juliet, [their] hearts are often frustrated, confused and in a mess,&rdquo; he concluded. &ldquo;But she takes all those feelings, calms them down, and reads them back to you as a beautiful song that&rsquo;s easier to understand.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\">(<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">WATCH</span>&nbsp;the Great Big Story video below)</p>\r\n<p><iframe id=\"widget2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/puPxDnSYJYU?rel=0&amp;enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=https:%2F%2Fwww.goodnewsnetwork.org\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">Friends, Romans, Countrymen! Be Sure And Share This With Your Friends On Social Media&hellip;</span></p>', 'posts/November2019/lFRAukUAk4Y1fdJxXuHa.jpg', 'dozens-of-volunteers-answer-the-world-s-most-forlorn-love-letters-addressed-to-shakespeare-s-juliet-by-mckinley-corbley-nov-3-2019', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2019-11-08 03:39:34', '2019-12-10 17:39:00', 6);
