(31, 1, 1, 'How the Salvation Army’s Red Kettles Became a Christmas Tradition', NULL, 'Tinseled trees and snowy landscapes are not the only signs of the upcoming holiday season.', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">Tinseled trees and snowy landscapes are not the only signs of the upcoming holiday season. Red kettles, staffed by men and women in street clothes, Santa suits and Salvation Army uniforms, also telegraph Christmastime.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">The Salvation Army is among America&rsquo;s top-grossing charities. In 2018, its 25,000&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"https://www.salvationarmyusa.org/usn/story/the-salvation-armys-2018-holiday-fundraising-season-raises-4337-million/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">bell-ringers helped raise</a>&nbsp;US$142.7 million. That was part of the charity&rsquo;s $3.8 billion year-end revenue from bequests, grants, sales, in-kind donations and investments as well as direct contributions.</p>\r\n<div id=\"smg-zone-smg-post-body-1\" class=\"smg-zone smg-zone-smg-post-body-1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 2.75rem; margin-bottom: 2.75rem; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px;\" data-gtm-vis-first-on-screen-9202037_141=\"6293\" data-gtm-vis-total-visible-time-9202037_141=\"1000\" data-gtm-vis-has-fired-9202037_141=\"1\">\r\n<div class=\"smg-zone-group smg-zone-group-monetized-post-body-1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: auto;\">\r\n<div class=\"smg-zone-widget smg-zone-widget-ads-blockthrough  \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n<div id=\"_5bf30c498c-186-2\" class=\"snopes-bt\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\">\r\n<div id=\"_5bf30c498c-186-2-container\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><iframe id=\"5bf30c498c-186-2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: relative; outline: none; margin: 2.75rem auto; display: block;\" src=\"https://www.btserve.com/render?ifrId=5bf30c498c-186-2&amp;code=5bf30c498c-186&amp;t=bidt-sra&amp;auctionId=42996f37-4dfe-41b6-a052-69f0195813df|5bf30c498c-186|2&amp;v2=true&amp;passback=false&amp;btserve=true\" width=\"728\" height=\"90\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation allow-popups\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"smg-zone-widget smg-zone-widget-ads-freestar  \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 2.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">William Booth, an English evangelist,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"https://www.christianitytoday.com/history/people/activists/william-booth.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">founded the Salvation Army</a>&nbsp;in 1878 as a religious outreach to London&rsquo;s poor. How a British evangelical church became an American icon is an&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674003965\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ongoing interest</a>&nbsp;of mine.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: \'IBM Plex Serif\', serif; line-height: 1.2; font-size: calc(1.3125rem + 0.78571vw); color: #252525;\">Entry into the United States</h2>\r\n<figure class=\"align-right \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px;\"><img class=\"lazy-resource\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: middle; height: auto; max-width: 100%; display: inline;\" src=\"https://images.theconversation.com/files/247609/original/file-20181127-76770-1yhn1zq.jpg?ixlib=rb-1.1.0&amp;q=45&amp;auto=format&amp;w=237&amp;fit=clip\" alt=\"\" data-lazy-loaded=\"true\" />\r\n<figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: small;\"><span class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">William Booth, founder of the Salvation Army.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><span class=\"attribution\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a class=\"source\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://www.apimages.com/metadata/Index/Associated-Press-Domestic-News-England-WILLIAM-BOOTH/918d8477b3e6da11af9f0014c2589dfb/1/0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">AP Photo</a></span></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">Booth, who called himself &ldquo;The General,&rdquo; fashioned his army on Britain&rsquo;s military. From the start, his &ldquo;soldiers&rdquo; wore uniforms, and they described their mission in martial terms. Salvationists&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"http://the-east-end.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">marched through the streets of London&rsquo;s East End</a>, a neighborhood of poor immigrants, with brass bands and female preachers. Booth and his followers also pursued &ldquo;sinners&rdquo; and frequently preached in bars, brothels and theaters.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">Booth&rsquo;s plan was to send his army worldwide, and his first stop was the United States. One of his early recruits had migrated to Philadelphia and&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674003965\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">wrote to Booth</a>&nbsp;about the residents&rsquo; need for salvation. In 1880, a small party of British Salvationists&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"http://www.castlegarden.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">debarked at Castle Garden</a>, New York&rsquo;s first immigration center. The group immediately started singing hymns set to popular melodies and marching through lower Manhattan.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">During the next few days, the&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"http://creatingdigitalhistory.wikidot.com/harry-hill-s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">English &ldquo;soldiers&rdquo; tacked up posters</a>, similar to ads for commercial entertainment, for a prayer service at Harry Hill&rsquo;s, a popular dance hall, theater and saloon. Not only was the venue thick with drunkards, prostitutes and pleasure seekers; its unlikeliness as a religious meeting place&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674003965\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">guaranteed press attention</a>.</p>\r\n<div id=\"smg-zone-smg-post-body-2\" class=\"smg-zone smg-zone-smg-post-body-2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 2.75rem; margin-bottom: 2.75rem; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px;\" data-gtm-vis-first-on-screen-9202037_141=\"39392\" data-gtm-vis-total-visible-time-9202037_141=\"1000\" data-gtm-vis-has-fired-9202037_141=\"1\">\r\n<div class=\"smg-zone-group smg-zone-group-monetized-post-body-2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: auto;\">\r\n<div class=\"smg-zone-widget smg-zone-widget-ads-blockthrough  \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n<div id=\"_5bf30c50a6-186-3\" class=\"snopes-bt\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\">\r\n<div id=\"_5bf30c50a6-186-3-container\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><iframe id=\"5bf30c50a6-186-3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: relative; outline: none; margin: 2.75rem auto; display: block;\" src=\"https://www.btserve.com/render?ifrId=5bf30c50a6-186-3&amp;code=5bf30c50a6-186&amp;t=bidt-sra&amp;auctionId=42996f37-4dfe-41b6-a052-69f0195813df|5bf30c50a6-186|3&amp;v2=true&amp;passback=false&amp;btserve=true\" width=\"728\" height=\"90\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation allow-popups\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"smg-zone-widget smg-zone-widget-ads-freestar  \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 2.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">Such unexpected behavior did bring the Salvation Army to the public&rsquo;s attention. Their boisterousness, even in service of saving souls, was criticized by New York&rsquo;s clergy and&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674003965\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ridiculed in newspapers and magazines</a>. That the Salvation Army featured female preachers at a time when most Protestant groups did not ordain women only added to its notoriety.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">But the army did not surrender. Pressing their &ldquo;invasion&rdquo; beyond New York City, the soldiers traveled first to Philadelphia and later nationwide. Their exuberance attracted young people and women to the cause.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">Young people liked the notion of a military crusade for religious purposes, and women joined because the Salvation Army&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"https://www.wlupress.wlu.ca/Books/W/Women-in-God-s-Army\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">offered them positions of leadership and authority</a>. In fact,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"https://socialwelfare.library.vcu.edu/people/booth-maud-ballington\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">William Booth&rsquo;s daughter-in-law, Maud Ballington,</a>&nbsp;followed by his two daughters,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"http://www.newfrontierchronicle.org/emma-booth-tucker-the-consul/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Emma</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"https://www.learningtogive.org/resources/booth-evangeline\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Evangeline</a>, headed the American Salvation Army from 1887 to 1950.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: \'IBM Plex Serif\', serif; line-height: 1.2; font-size: calc(1.3125rem + 0.78571vw); color: #252525;\">Kettles for Christmas dinner</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">In both Britain and the U.S., Salvationists saw their mission as twofold: converting sinners and assisting the needy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674003965\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">In the Salvation Army&rsquo;s perspective</a>, the two went hand in hand, which is why members opened shelters for addicts, alcoholics and prostitutes. Yet they also sought to aid &ldquo;down and outers,&rdquo; their name for the needy. Among their early outreaches were Christmas dinners for the urban poor. But finding funds for food and gifts was difficult.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"align-center \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px;\"><img class=\"lazy-resource\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: middle; height: auto; max-width: 100%; display: inline;\" src=\"https://images.theconversation.com/files/247560/original/file-20181127-76764-1jt5lo.jpg?ixlib=rb-1.1.0&amp;q=45&amp;auto=format&amp;w=754&amp;fit=clip\" alt=\"\" data-lazy-loaded=\"true\" />\r\n<figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: small;\"><span class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Salvation Army mini Red Kettle and bell at Delnor-Wiggins Pass State Park.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><span class=\"attribution\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a class=\"source\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/130946855@N03/24815413578/in/photolist-DNRtUf-DN3nKL-H196PR-21T3LGJ-q38Vgg-pSoPmx-ZAgYZg-GZfFQk-21T3SNS-GZfGDV-tEy6R-dBpJiW-GZgphP-ZQraxh-DN3kim-H18NqT-21RLYbC-21VTJNH-ZAgSyv-21T4Ncq-21RM7J9-ZzsKtx-ZQrHmN-ZzsEZT-DN3juC-DN1JuL-H19eXp-DNRw7G-21QWDKq-91w3jw-aYjpPz-aYjqsZ-aXp7uB-aYjqAv-aYjprF-aYjpFc-aYjqQP-21QW69y-21VUPKe-DN2JyS-ZQqV9s-H19d7a-DNRhf3-21VSKB8-ZztVya-GZfozt-GZgmZn-DN1KCs-21WLJ1P-H18PC2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Robin Wendell/Flickr.com</a>,&nbsp;<a class=\"license\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CC BY</a></span></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id=\"smg-zone-smg-post-body-3\" class=\"smg-zone smg-zone-smg-post-body-3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 2.75rem; margin-bottom: 2.75rem; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px;\" data-gtm-vis-first-on-screen-9202037_141=\"43053\" data-gtm-vis-total-visible-time-9202037_141=\"1000\" data-gtm-vis-has-fired-9202037_141=\"1\">\r\n<div class=\"smg-zone-group smg-zone-group-monetized-post-body-3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: auto;\">\r\n<div class=\"smg-zone-widget smg-zone-widget-ads-blockthrough  \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n<div id=\"_5bf30d1fd9-186-4\" class=\"snopes-bt\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\">\r\n<div id=\"_5bf30d1fd9-186-4-container\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><iframe id=\"5bf30d1fd9-186-4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: relative; outline: none; margin: 2.75rem auto; display: block;\" src=\"https://www.btserve.com/render?ifrId=5bf30d1fd9-186-4&amp;code=5bf30d1fd9-186&amp;t=bidt-sra&amp;auctionId=42996f37-4dfe-41b6-a052-69f0195813df|5bf30d1fd9-186|4&amp;v2=true&amp;passback=false&amp;btserve=true\" width=\"728\" height=\"90\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation allow-popups\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"smg-zone-widget smg-zone-widget-ads-freestar  \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 2.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">By 1891, Salvationists had outposts nationwide. In San Francisco, Salvation Army Captain Joseph McFee was eager to serve a Christmas feast for a thousand of the city&rsquo;s poorest residents. Frustrated by his lack of success,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674003965\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">he decided to improvise</a>. Grabbing a crab pot from the local wharf, he hung it from a tripod at a busy intersection. Above the pot was a sign: &ldquo;Fill the Pot for the Poor &mdash; Free Dinner on Christmas Day.&rdquo; McFee&rsquo;s campaign was a success.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">Word spread and the kettles soon&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674003965\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">provided Christmas dinners</a>&nbsp;for thousands nationwide.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">The kettle also helped&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674003965\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">rehabilitate the Salvation Army&rsquo;s image</a>. Instead of seeing Salvationists as an unruly pack of religious rebels, many Americans recognized their work with the poor. At a time when neither state nor federal governments provided a social safety net,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books/about/Marching_to_Glory.html?id=-YjZAAAAMAAJ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">the Salvation Army offered</a>&nbsp;meals, beds, work and medical facilities to destitute men and women.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">But it was the Salvationists&rsquo; service in World War I that sealed the deal. Eager to support the American war effort, Salvation Army leaders sent &ldquo;Sallies,&rdquo; the popular nickname for army women, to the French front. The Sallies set up huts where they&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"https://www.smithsonianmag.com/history/donut-girls-wwi-helped-fill-soldiers-bellies-and-get-women-vote-180962864/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">fried donuts</a>, sewed buttons, wrote letters and otherwise &ldquo;mothered&rdquo; the troops.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">The women&rsquo;s faith, fortitude and friendship touched many young soldiers.&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #939394; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: #fbd440 0px -2px 0px inset;\" href=\"http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674003965\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">One wrote in his letter home:</a></p>\r\n<blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 2.75rem -2.75rem 0px; position: relative; border-width: 0px; font-family: \'IBM Plex Serif\', serif; padding: 2.75rem; background: rgba(251, 212, 64, 0.2); color: #252525; font-size: 16px;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 1rem;\">&ldquo;These good women create an atmosphere that reminds us of home, and out of the millions of men over there not one ever dreams of offering the slightest sign of disrespect or lack of consideration to these wonderful women.&rdquo;</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 2.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #252525; font-family: \'IBM Plex Sans\', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';\">By the war&rsquo;s end, the Salvation Army had become a symbol of American humanitarianism, and fundraising was much easier. But after the 1920s, the army&rsquo;s evangelical crusade took a back seat to social service delivery, at least in their public relations. It was easier to raise money for helping the poor than for converting them.</p>', 'posts/December2019/5Kj9uATwo3OJn6Buislq.jpg', 'how-the-salvation-army-s-red-kettles-became-a-christmas-tradition', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED', 1, '2019-12-06 08:15:01', '2019-12-10 17:35:51', 23);

